{"tid":846361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"擺兩三圍酒 ，算唔算擺酒？","createTime":"2018-10-03T11:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T11:25:48.000Z","uid":149324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29d4a5fb43a9750c679efb2e0ca30d6afcde78b9","tid":846361,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"如果結婚只係擺兩三圍酒，唔係叫擺酒？<br />\n只係係叫食飯？"},{"pid":"2044bc024ac64eec4ea84421ba76f4c0cec1d73c","tid":846361,"uid":85557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"通常兩三圍嗰啲都叫和頭酒"},{"pid":"df399f25dc813acc20cc7919db0004c79bf005ac","tid":846361,"uid":115082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"你自己都識講擺二三圍酒<br />\n咁唔係擺酒叫乜"},{"pid":"ca66e157b34587010c456f3302ede06fefa23222","tid":846361,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常兩三圍嗰啲都叫和頭酒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n,『和頭酒』的用途乃是透過擺筵席,而後冰釋原本有嫌隙的兩方之間的仇恨,化敵為友,而過往的恩恩怨怨亦在酒席上一筆勾銷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和頭酒唔係用來化解恩怨咩？"},{"pid":"b4d07a2bdd59f6e0d4b0f6a1f7967dba38228a81","tid":846361,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己都識講擺二三圍酒<br />\n咁唔係擺酒叫乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我頭先到老豆老母罵我讀咁多年書都唔知咩係擺酒，佢地話兩三圍個d就叫食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79aa8e6b477c8d08bad170993bee87a391e53daf","tid":846361,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:15:14.000Z","msg":"算<br />\n你再擺少d 淨係請親戚就最撚好添<br />\n我真係恭喜你呀 <br />\n<br />\n唔俾帖我ge哥布林才是好哥布林 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098b9a38e6f9e5f434e7fcf8fe6efee2f28931cb","tid":846361,"uid":85557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca66e157b34587010c456f3302ede06fefa23222","tid":846361,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:11:37.000Z",